  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Three methods including flow cytometry, next generation sequencing and determination of
      circulating tumor cells will be performed at different time points in patients with
      previously undiagnosed multiple myeloma in order to determine the most sensitive method to
      detect residual disease
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
